{"tid":273063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打覺得ATM櫃員機先退卡再出錢呢下好返人類？","createTime":"2017-06-06T09:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T11:01:03.000Z","uid":114183,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9e4b0e3c547ea7e5e9bb4b9fc2333763734bbe","tid":273063,"uid":114183,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:31:34.000Z","msg":"Dllm 已經唔係第一次試過拎咗卡跟住唔記得拎錢就走咗人 咁就又唔見咗兩舊水<br />\n雖然話多唔多話少唔少<br />\n但係咁樣就無咗兩舊 仲要益埋人地<br />\n其實係咪可以報警？<br />\n錢追唔追得返有無我都無所謂<br />\n最主要係要想捉到執錢條友<br />\n然後要佢知道自己貪小便宜其實都犯緊法<br />\n點解ATM唔可以先出錢後退卡？<br />\n因為錢一唔見就係搵唔返<br />\n卡唔見都可以話即時報失同補領<br />\n同埋提款卡有密碼<br />\n錢都唔會俾人㩒走啩？<br />\n同埋出錢位係下面<br />\n退卡位係上面<br />\n好多時真係拎完卡就唔記得下面出錢<br />\n我知道係我大頭蝦<br />\n但係我覺得如果調轉下應該會好啲咯<br />\n起碼唔洗一嘢就唔見咗啲錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef436245514809537721c53bc825435bc473a18","tid":273063,"uid":119302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:33:42.000Z","msg":"自己拎左卡無拎錢就走左仲上黎吠 <br />\n果然係世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35c4d68b324ff727a643bc1646e03909fa06b01","tid":273063,"uid":52839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:34:34.000Z","msg":"無拎錢唔打返去銀行 樓豬係咪戇鳩"},{"pid":"89aa2e00b62cd5cef55877c98e495e9631086f84","tid":273063,"uid":58649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:37:09.000Z","msg":"樓豬on9<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b96e85719d0d8eb27f42ab759c28fa5c94a971","tid":273063,"uid":18430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:37:43.000Z","msg":"唔覺，係你廢"},{"pid":"32529066dd3f89f710338a2e910632d2f61956a1","tid":273063,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:37:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬on9<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e7ae8b250f35c5a65d022c11e27c6ab77744a9a4","tid":273063,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:38:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓豬on9<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\nX2"},{"pid":"6b15a940353df6cda63d1411173ad237d2cec9f1","tid":273063,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:39:09.000Z","msg":"錢都可以唔記得拎 on9"},{"pid":"095d4860e9975f7f6e52e1862b0be9a4f8ddd155","tid":273063,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"去攞錢既目的係咩?<br />\n去攞錢跟住唔記得攞錢係咪好反人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c17aa21be58f2d5202b2cc616133dba2a07d490","tid":273063,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:41:32.000Z","msg":"人地咁設計係有原因，<br />\n唔見卡緊要D 定唔見提款緊要D?<br />\n<br />\n你老母生你出黎就真係反人類"},{"pid":"b29b2110044b3499af41dd45f8c2c810933b23b8","tid":273063,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:43:45.000Z","msg":"唔覺, 你笨啫"},{"pid":"9f6fb44b00b18758d3f59d557b0de9a2ada4b446","tid":273063,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:43:59.000Z","msg":"調轉左你又會唔記得拎卡<br />\n你諗下 好多人會好似你咁唔記得拎錢 幾百就算尻數 但唔撚見左張卡就無得算尻數 變相銀行會收多好多電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc943cf00482dbc05f5a5157db374d46e441ab6","tid":273063,"uid":45000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:50:37.000Z","msg":"因為唔見卡大鍋過唔見錢<br />\n如果撳完錢唔記得拎，部機會食返，如果比人拎左，去分行填表，會睇返CCTV，有機會銀行報驚<br />\n如果唔記得拎卡，後面個條友有機會見到你個密碼"},{"pid":"f74f8a58a6ebedade9d6cd61dbb4314fd9fd5b21","tid":273063,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:50:56.000Z","msg":"你弱智？"},{"pid":"3ee74f2679a1f05d65dfc08916f35ac87d163c71","tid":273063,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:51:03.000Z","msg":"第一 去Atm拎錢係最終目的 <br />\n第二 唔記得拎卡嘅潛在損失大啲<br />\n所以拎完卡先拎錢 先最附合人性"},{"pid":"d5d399624a13bd5e50629ece6f779ff516e07acb","tid":273063,"uid":19948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:52:20.000Z","msg":"到時出錢再出卡 <br />\n你無拎卡咪又係上嚟屌"},{"pid":"ff35c15d63731e4031a0bbfa1783f8f74af34086","tid":273063,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:54:09.000Z","msg":"錢同卡一次過好似麵包機咁一野射出嚟好唔好呀屌你？"},{"pid":"9242540ba31689934799b29d1f2985f9c140d40f","tid":273063,"uid":109889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:55:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錢同卡一次過好似麵包機咁一野射出嚟好唔好呀屌你？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61138b1f43fc6c4ba004215c9c2b0429c9771fc","tid":273063,"uid":45000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到時出錢再出卡 <br />\n你無拎卡咪又係上嚟屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDllm 已經唔係第一次試過拎咗錢跟住唔記得拎卡就走咗人 咁就又唔見咗一舊水補領新卡<br />\n雖然話多唔多話少唔少<br />\n但係咁樣就無咗一舊 仲要益埋銀行<br />\n其實係咪可以報警？<br />\n卡追唔追得返有無我都無所謂<br />\n最主要係要想捉到執卡條友<br />\n然後要佢知道自己貪小便宜其實都犯緊法<br />\n點解ATM唔可以先出卡後出錢？<br />\n因為卡一唔見就係搵唔返<br />\n錢唔見都可以話即時報警<br />\n同埋錢有NUMBER<br />\n卡都唔會俾人㩒走啩？<br />\n同埋出錢位係下面<br />\n退卡位係上面<br />\n好多時真係拎完錢就唔記得上面拎卡<br />\n我知道係我大頭蝦<br />\n但係我覺得如果調轉下應該會好啲咯<br />\n起碼唔洗一嘢就唔見咗張卡先"},{"pid":"1efd354fbe5bcecf0d4e258929a0ffe90fba50ef","tid":273063,"uid":9735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"先出卡唔出錢 係因為仲多人會一拎左錢就唔記得拎卡⋯<br />\n人人都係為左拎錢先去撳機，潛意識會錢一到手，任務完成就走得，調返轉，出卡先，你會記得你目的都未達成，你會等埋拎錢先走，如果你唔記得拎錢，只怪你on 9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4468448d60b73fc189da22271cd561aee1b3ae","tid":273063,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:04:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錢同卡一次過好似麵包機咁一野射出嚟好唔好呀屌你？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df3114cc1913aeefd48da6ffa6e055f7abbc0ae","tid":273063,"uid":79588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:59:08.000Z","msg":"唔記得拎錢 唔一定會比人拎左<br />\n除非你後面有成村人排隊啦<br />\n如果冇人拎嘅話 有機會佢會食返入去部機到(部分銀行)<br />\n你打簿就一定係扣左錢(就算佢食番入去)<br />\n你有疑問就去櫃位問啦 填張form 比番資料佢嘅話有機會入返比你"},{"pid":"f63513aa86ee53e5796ac464bfc0870763b3a8f5","tid":273063,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"拎200蚊好笑<br />\n唔記得拎好笑"}]}